OL,3,CRower dreads being covered in sewage
OL,4,Cif she capsizes in the River Thames
OL,6,FA rower described how she dreads the
OL,7,Fthought of capsizing in the Thames
OL,8,Fbecause of the risk of getting covered
OL,9,Fin sewage.
OL,11,FSaratu Audu frequently rows through
OL,12,Fthe river in south west London with
OL,13,Fother members of the Fulham Reach Boat
OL,14,FClub.
OL,16,FBut on the day regulator Ofwat
OL,17,Fproposed #168 million worth of fines
OL,18,Ffor three of England's biggest water
OL,19,Fcompanies for failing to limit river
OL,20,Fpollution, Saratu said she often "saw
OL,21,Fstuff floating about".
