OL,3,CRower dreads being covered in sewage
OL,4,Cif she capsizes in the River Thames
OL,6,FShe added: "It's poo together with fat
OL,7,Fand sometimes it's branches and twigs
OL,8,Fand it's awful to look at and it does
OL,9,Fmake you feel, oh my God, I hope I
OL,10,Fdon't capsize today because if I do
OL,11,FI'm literally going to have poo all
OL,12,Fover me.
OL,14,F"When it rains it's really horrible,
OL,15,Fit floats around the tops of the boats
OL,16,Fas well.
OL,18,F"So that's one of the things we have
OL,19,Fto do. We have to wash boats after
OL,20,Fevery session because it's you
OL,21,Factually see it.
