OL,3,CRower dreads being covered in sewage
OL,4,Cif she capsizes in the River Thames
OL,6,F"You see the scum on the side of your
OL,7,Fboat and beneath it."
OL,9,FSaratu said she had to put her rowing
OL,10,Fkit on a hot wash each time she went
OL,11,Fout on the river. Her club also has
OL,12,Fshowers to help maintain hygiene.
OL,14,FRegulator Ofwat proposed the fine for
OL,15,FThames, plus sanctions of #47 million
OL,16,Ffor Yorkshire Water and #17 million
OL,17,Ffor Northumbrian Water, in the first
OL,18,Fresults of a landmark probe into all
OL,19,F11 of England and Wales' water firms.
