OL,3,CRower dreads being covered in sewage
OL,4,Cif she capsizes in the River Thames
OL,6,FOfwat chief executive David Black
OL,7,Fcalled the three firms' records of
OL,8,Fpolluting rivers and waterways "a
OL,9,Fcatalogue of failure".
OL,11,FHe said: "Our investigation has shown
OL,12,Fhow they routinely released sewage
OL,13,Finto our rivers and seas, rather than
OL,14,Fensuring that this only happens in
OL,15,Fexceptional circumstances as the law
OL,16,Fintends."
