OL,3,CRower dreads being covered in sewage
OL,4,Cif she capsizes in the River Thames
OL,6,FWater companies have faced public
OL,7,Foutrage over the extent of pollution,
OL,8,Fand at a lack of investment in water
OL,9,Finfrastructure, rising bills, high
OL,10,Fdividends and executive pay and
OL,11,Fbonuses at privatised water firms.
OL,13,FThe fine could be especially impactful
OL,14,Ffor Thames, which is in the grip of a
OL,15,Ffunding crisis and has more than #15
OL,16,Fbillion of debt. It said last month
OL,17,Fthat it only has enough money to
OL,18,Fcontinue trading until the end of May
OL,19,F2025.
